      "raw_text": "The fall session of the Holy\nNames Normal School opens\nSept. s, 1909. 1t will be under\nthe same management as in for\nmer years. The Academic Class\nes will be resumed on Sept. 8,\n1909. The Primary and Gram\nmar Grades of Holy Names\nTraining School and the Music\nGlasses Of Piano, Harp, Violin\nand Voice Culture will be re-\nsumed Sept. 7, 1909. Apply for\nyear book to Sister Superior."
